AWP_Aztec_Lego_HF
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
by Miguel "I-Iybr1d" Silveira
Sponsored by http://www.fragxl.com

Description:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
It's a simple awp lego based map with aztec design with
a buyzone in the center.
It wasn't a hard map to make since the idea isn't new nor the concept,
plus, it took only a few number or hours to make, so...

Map Info: 1 BuyZone, 32 Spawns, Soundscapes and 3D skybox
Build Time: 24 hours
Tools used: Hammer Editor, Photoshop CS2 + VTF Plugin, VTF Edit, PackRat

Story:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Aliens came down to our place and taught the aztec culture
how to build pyramids with... Yes, you guess it right! Lego bricks!

Notes and Contact:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Contacts: Visit www.fragxl.com and http://hfusion.planetaclix.pt
Copyright Notes: Credit to Boharox for his great lego texture pack
and TopHATTwaffle for giving us great tutorials.
Many thanks to Unreal and FragXL community

Miguel "I-Iybr1d" Silveira 10/09/2010
